-> class objects constructor kya hota hai ye sab pata hai to uske bare mai example nahi likh rha hoo.....



-> in python how to declare constructor:
	
	class Employee:	
		def __init__(self,sal,ag):

			self.salary=sal
			self.age=ag

	e1=Employee(24000,21)
	e2=Employee(26000,23)


	note: def __init__() is tarike se constructor declare hota hai python mai....

	-> self: self ek memory address hota hai object ka like e1 is object of class to el ka memory address hota. memory address hexadecimal hota hai like 2234 aesa...

		note:self keyword dena compulsory hai pytho mai....

	-> self.salary: self.salary ka matlab ye hota hai vo memory address leta hai objects ka uske help se vo salary name ka  variable create karega....

	-> def: def keyword se function create hota hai in python.... 


-> in oops there are two variables 

	1): Instance Variables: instance variables ka matlab alag alag objects ke alag alag values is called instance variables.... alag alag copies banegi aur alag alag values hogi.....

		note: agar aapne ek object mai change kiya to baki sab objects mai change nahi hoga.

	2): Class Variables: class variables ka matlab ek hi copy create hota sab object ke liye is called class variables. class variables is made for all objects...

		note: but class variables mai koi bhi object mai modify or change nahi hoga...
			  object ke madad se aap class variable mai change nahi kar sakte par class se kar sakte ho...



-> instance mehods are setter or getter method:

	-> setter method to set the values of insatnce variables...
	-> getter method to get the values of insatnce variables...

